    AnnotatedDocument
    Models a record in the annotated_document table.
    DefaultAlignmentDocument
    Models the contents of the plugin_document_xml column in case the root element is <DefaultAlignmentDocument>.
    Document
    Standard Java Bean reflecting the contents of the document_xml column within the annotated_document table.
    DocumentClass
    An enumeration of a possible values for the "class" attribute of the <document> element in the document_xml column.
    DocumentNotes
    A DocumentNotes instance maintains the values of all relevant notes within the document_xml column.
    DocumentNotes.Note
    Enumerates all XML elements that contain a note that might be used for OAI-PMH generation.
    IAnnotatedDocumentPostFilter
    Filters records from the annotated_document table after they have been converted to AnnotatedDocument instances.
    IAnnotatedDocumentPreFilter
    Filters records from the annotated_document table before they are converted from raw database result set data to AnnotatedDocument instances.
    IAnnotatedDocumentSetFilter
    A set filter filters out annotated_document records within the context of the entire set of records retrieved from the database.
    PluginDocument 
    XMLSerialisableRootElement
    Models the contents of the plugin_document_xml column in case the root element is <XMLSerialisableRootElement>.
